A Gout Tuber Plant has a chance of appearing after hacking down jungle in the Tai Bwo Wannai Cleanup minigame. It can be harvested by using a Spade on it, giving the player a Gout tuber.

Attempting to dig up a Gout Tuber Plant uncovered by another player results in the message, "It's not yours to dig.". They will despawn after 10 minutes if not dug up. Gout tubers are locked to the player that found them for the duration that the player is logged in. As soon as the original owner of the tuber logs out, any player is able to dig up the tuber. The tuber will not re-lock to the original owner if the player logs back in. As soon as a player begins to dig up the tuber, it becomes locked to them and no one else is able to dig it up.

A '''Gout Tuber Plant''' has a chance of appearing after hacking down jungle in the [[Tai Bwo Wannai Cleanup]] [[minigame]]. It can be harvested by using a [[Spade]] on it, giving the player a [[Gout tuber]]. 

Attempting to dig up a Gout Tuber Plant uncovered by another player results in the message, "It's not yours to dig.". They will despawn after 10 minutes if not dug up. Gout tubers are locked to the player that found them for the duration that the player is logged in. As soon as the original owner of the tuber logs out, any player is able to dig up the tuber. The tuber will not re-lock to the original owner if the player logs back in. As soon as a player begins to dig up the tuber, it becomes locked to them and no one else is able to dig it up.
